===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}

{{Han compound|刀|alt1=刂|𡰯|alt2=𡰯|ls=psc|c1=s|c2=p|t1=knife}}. It represents the act of shaving something flat with a knife, and by extension, is used to convey the meanings of "to scrape" or "to print."<ref>Digital Shinjigen 2017</ref>

