===Etymology===
Perhaps from {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*srəwt|t=to wipe, sweep, rub, scrub}} (STEDT, under PTB *s(u/i)t). Cognate with {{cog|bo|བཤུད|t=to wipe}}, {{cog|my|သုတ်|t=idem}}<ref>{{R:sit:Luce 1981|page=51|head=-UT Finals (22. to Wipe)}}</ref> (though STEDT mistakenly puts down {{och-l|恤|to sympathize, compensate}} for the Chinese character instead).

